<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>InfinixPlus+ | Premium Loan Solutions in Singapore</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-dark: #2D1B69;
            --primary-light: #6B46C1;
            --accent: #FF6B35;
            --accent-light: #FF9F68;
            --accent-glow: #FF8C42;
            --dark: #0A0A0A;
            --darker: #050505;
            --light: #F5F5F5;
            --gray: #6C757D;
        }
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        }
        
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--darker), #1a1a2e);
            color: var(--light);
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        
        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 15px;
        }
        
        /* Header & Navigation */
        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark), #1a1a2e);
            color: white;
            padding: 1rem 0;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }
        
        .header-container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
        }
        
        .logo-text {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .logo-infinix {
            color: #8B5CF6; /* Purple color */
        }
        
        .logo-plus {
            color: white;
        }
        
        .logo-circle {
            width: 55px;
            height: 55px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-light), var(--accent-glow));
            border-radius: 12px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.6), 0 0 20px rgba(255, 140, 66, 0.4);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        
        .logo-circle::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -50%;
            left: -50%;
            width: 200%;
            height: 200%;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.1), transparent);
            transform: rotate(45deg);
            animation: shine 3s infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes shine {
            0% { transform: translateX(-100%) translateY(-100%) rotate(45deg); }
            100% { transform: translateX(100%) translateY(100%) rotate(45deg); }
        }
        
        nav ul {
            display: flex;
            list-style: none;
            gap: 2rem;
        }
        
        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            position: relative;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
        }
        
        nav a:hover {
            color: var(--accent-light);
        }
        
        nav a::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -5px;
            left: 0;
            width: 0;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-light));
            transition: width 0.3s;
        }
        
        nav a:hover::after {
            width: 100%;
        }
        
        .mobile-menu {
            display: none;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        
        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.9), rgba(20, 20, 30, 0.9)), url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1554224155-6726b3ff858f?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            color: white;
            padding: 8rem 0;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .hero::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.1), rgba(30, 30, 40, 0.3));
            z-index: 0;
        }
        
        .hero .container {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff, #e0e0ff);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        
        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
            color: #e0e0ff;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-light));
            color: white;
            padding: 14px 35px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 700;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.4);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.6);
        }
        
        .btn:disabled {
            background: #cccccc;
            cursor: not-allowed;
            transform: none;
            box-shadow: none;
        }
        
        /* Loading Spinner */
        .spinner {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            border: 3px solid rgba(255,255,255,.3);
            border-radius: 50%;
            border-top-color: #fff;
            animation: spin 1s ease-in-out infinite;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        
        @keyframes spin {
            to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }
        
        /* Sections */
        section {
            padding: 6rem 0;
        }
        
        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }
        
        .section-title h2 {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff, #b8b8ff);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        
        .section-title h2::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -12px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 100px;
            height: 5px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-light));
            border-radius: 3px;
        }
        
        .section-title p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #b8b8ff;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        /* Features */
        .features {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0f23, #1a1a2e);
        }
        
        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
            gap: 2.5rem;
        }
        
        .feature-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(45, 27, 105, 0.3), rgba(74, 47, 163, 0.2));
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            transition: all 0.4s;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }
        
        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-12px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(45, 27, 105, 0.4);
            border-color: rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.3);
        }
        
        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-light));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        
        .feature-card h3 {
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .feature-card p {
            color: #b8b8ff;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
        }
        
        /* Loan Products */
        .products {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #0f0f23);
        }
        
        .products-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2.5rem;
        }
        
        .product-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(45, 27, 105, 0.4), rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.6));
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            transition: all 0.4s;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .product-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 5px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-light));
        }
        
        .product-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(45, 27, 105, 0.5);
        }
        
        .product-icon {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-light));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        
        .product-card h3 {
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .product-details {
            text-align: left;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .product-details ul {
            list-style: none;
        }
        
        .product-details li {
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
            color: #b8b8ff;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .product-details li i {
            color: var(--accent);
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
        
        /* Loan Calculator */
        .calculator {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark), #1a1a2e);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .calculator::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551288049-bebda4e38f71?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            opacity: 0.1;
        }
        
        .calculator-container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 3rem;
            align-items: center;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        
        .calculator-form {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
        }
        
        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .form-control {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            background: white;
            color: #333;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        
        .form-control:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--accent);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.3);
        }
        
        .form-control::placeholder {
            color: #888;
        }
        
        .range-value {
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 8px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        
        .calculator-result {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2.5rem;
            background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.7);
            border-radius: 15px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }
        
        .result-amount {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-light));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        
        .result-details {
            margin: 1.5rem 0;
        }
        
        .result-details p {
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
            color: #b8b8ff;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        
        .result-details span {
            color: white;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        /* Application Form */
        .application {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0f23, #1a1a2e);
        }
        
        .application-form {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            padding: 3rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            color: #333;
        }
        
        .form-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 1.5rem;
        }
        
        .application-form .form-group label {
            color: #333;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .application-form .form-control {
            background: white;
            color: #333;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        
        .application-form .form-control:focus {
            border-color: var(--accent);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.2);
        }
        
        /* Success Message */
        .success-message {
            display: none;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4CAF50, #45a049);
            color: white;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-in;
        }
        
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        
        /* Testimonials */
        .testimonials {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #0f0f23);
        }
        
        .testimonial-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
            gap: 2.5rem;
        }
        
        .testimonial-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(45, 27, 105, 0.3), rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.6));
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            position: relative;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }
        
        .testimonial-card::before {
            content: """;
            font-size: 5rem;
            color: var(--accent);
            opacity: 0.2;
            position: absolute;
            top: -10px;
            left: 15px;
            line-height: 1;
            font-family: Georgia, serif;
        }
        
        .testimonial-text {
            margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #e0e0ff;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .testimonial-author {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1.2rem;
        }
        
        .author-avatar {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-light));
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }
        
        .author-info h4 {
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
        }
        
        .author-info p {
            color: #b8b8ff;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }
        
        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark), #0a0a15);
            color: white;
            padding: 5rem 0 2rem;
        }
        
        .footer-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }
        
        .footer-column h3 {
            margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
        }
        
        .footer-column h3::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 50px;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-light));
        }
        
        .footer-column ul {
            list-style: none;
        }
        
        .footer-column ul li {
            margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
        }
        
        .footer-column a {
            color: #b8b8ff;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }
        
        .footer-column a:hover {
            color: var(--accent-light);
        }
        
        .contact-info {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            color: #b8b8ff;
        }
        
        .contact-info i {
            color: var(--accent);
            width: 20px;
        }
        
        .copyright {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 2.5rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            color: #888;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }
        
        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 992px) {
            .calculator-container,
            .form-row {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.8rem;
            }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            nav ul {
                display: none;
                position: absolute;
                top: 100%;
                left: 0;
                width: 100%;
                background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--dark), #1a1a2e);
                flex-direction: column;
                padding: 1.5rem;
                box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
                text-align: center;
            }
            
            nav ul.active {
                display: flex;
            }
            
            .mobile-menu {
                display: block;
            }
            
            .hero {
                padding: 5rem 0;
            }
            
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.3rem;
            }
            
            section {
                padding: 4rem 0;
            }
            
            .application-form {
                padding: 2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <header>
        <div class="container header-container">
            <div class="logo">
                <div class="logo-circle">IP+</div>
                <div class="logo-text">
                    <span class="logo-infinix">Infinix</span>
                    <span class="logo-plus">Plus+</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <nav>
                <ul id="nav-menu">
                    <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#products">Loan Products</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#calculator">Calculator</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#application">Apply Now</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#testimonials">Testimonials</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
                </ul>
                <div class="mobile-menu" id="mobile-menu">
                    <i class="fas fa-bars"></i>
                </div>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero" id="home">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Premium Financial Solutions for Singapore's Future</h1>
            <p>InfinixPlus+ offers tailored loan options for individuals and businesses with industry-leading rates, lightning-fast approvals, and personalized service that puts you first.</p>
            <a href="#application" class="btn">Apply For Loan Today</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <section class="features">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2>Why Choose InfinixPlus+</h2>
                <p>Experience financial services redefined with our customer-centric approach</p>
            </div>
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-bolt"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Lightning-Fast Approval</h3>
                    <p>Get your loan approved within 4-6 hours with our fully digital application process. No lengthy paperwork, no unnecessary delays.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-percentage"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Unbeatable Rates</h3>
                    <p>Enjoy Singapore's most competitive interest rates starting from just 3.8% p.a. for qualified applicants across all loan types.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Bank-Level Security</h3>
                    <p>Your financial data is protected with 256-bit encryption and multi-factor authentication, ensuring complete peace of mind.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Loan Products -->
    <section class="products" id="products">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2>Our Premium Loan Products</h2>
                <p>Tailored financial solutions designed to meet your unique needs and aspirations</p>
            </div>
            <div class="products-grid">
                <div class="product-card">
                    <div class="product-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-user-tie"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Personal Excellence Loan</h3>
                    <p>Flexible financing for life's important moments</p>
                    <div class="product-details">
                        <ul>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Loan Amount: S$5,000 - S$200,000</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Interest Rate: 4.5% - 9.8% p.a.</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Flexible Terms: 1-7 years</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> No Collateral Required</li>
                            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Disbursement within 6 hours</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="product-card">
                    <div class="product-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-building"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Business Growth Loan</h3>
                    <p>Fuel your entrepreneurial dreams with capital</p>
                    <div class="product-details">
                        <ul>
